{"tid":358192,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣跑步有感","createTime":"2017-08-13T14:18:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T18:36:42.000Z","uid":126603,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b7b9f120b3d970191a7d57a7393b7e32bd6fec5e","tid":358192,"uid":126603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T14:18:36.000Z","msg":"我係一個肥宅。<br />\n由於俾好多fd話我太肥，於是我呢排決定去荃灣海旁跑步減肥。<br />\n雖然每次跑都有進步，但開始感覺到自己一個跑真係好悶。<br />\n平時冇男仔fd同我跑，更唔好講女仔fd，自己讀嗰科基本上唔會識到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n眼見海旁明明好多女仔跑步，但我冇機會識到，真係好sad。<br />\n今日聽住海旁有堆人播住周董d歌，只能說<br />\n<br />\n這些機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067be7299fbee72d7a213bf0108e5e73942b1313","tid":358192,"uid":6308,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T14:38:43.000Z","msg":"跑你就跑啦 跑步定識女仔？"},{"pid":"9935fa2a3b5068aa6376e95d122bd7c2f8449996","tid":358192,"uid":17835,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T14:46:43.000Z","msg":"好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53799786a61789d5e7a5f77f6f769996ba70e22","tid":358192,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T14:47:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跑你就跑啦 跑步定識女仔？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f04919d4a3792217591b803c7d879db0203052fe","tid":358192,"uid":58614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:01:16.000Z","msg":"之前覺得一個人跑好悶 <br />\n所以約咗d巴打出黎跑<br />\n跑完之後  都係自己跑正d <br />\n又可以一邊跑一邊聽歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b680c259d9fc9887572e42128b5c5b127640352d","tid":358192,"uid":126603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:47:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跑你就跑啦 跑步定識女仔？</blockquote><br />\n想搵個fd跑啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時你冇fd，結果逼住做你唔太鍾意嘅運動係一件好壓抑嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e876a856e58ad41bc77832a01720e41090f236d","tid":358192,"uid":126603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:49:32.000Z","msg":"咁多負皮，我都係自己做一個死肥宅獨自跑算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7732679b41fcf56d53a8c0f7fdfa4b82d778deb8","tid":358192,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:49:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2531361860c0162f484f82d12bd1f9757c2a260","tid":358192,"uid":126603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:50:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同人跑要就返速度好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都係既<br />\n利申：太肥，速度一般"},{"pid":"65518c83465ac23879d5753160396a910e55a99f","tid":358192,"uid":45142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:57:08.000Z","msg":"跑你就跑啦，d女唔係比你望"},{"pid":"7dafe461b5d260273309905b541077560e0d61a0","tid":358192,"uid":90000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T16:01:07.000Z","msg":"跑過去深井未呀？"},{"pid":"73391452d6d4d6e85d2fc40412318dc64d196651","tid":358192,"uid":126603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T17:08:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跑過去深井未呀？</blockquote><br />\n冇咁強嘅體力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我辣殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75c594ff1e1dd70621e204428af71b34e83170c","tid":358192,"uid":65265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T17:19:57.000Z","msg":"空氣好差已經唔跑海濱個頭，調返轉跑去近水灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc7ae38fb81710de68a9e2e56b382a0df49e2c3","tid":358192,"uid":131686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T17:22:41.000Z","msg":"我6點仲跑步🈶️好多美腿睇<img src=\"/asset